author: Fox News
title: Hawaii helicopter crash near Kauai missile facility draws military response, at least 4 dead
description: At least four people are dead after a civilian contracted helicopter crashed in Hawaii on Tuesday near the Pacific Missile Range Facility (PMRF) in Kauai County, according to the U.S. military.
